Substance Overview

(ELP0175_SubstanceOverview)

Description

This presentation provides an introduction to the scope and content of the Substance hierarchy.

Learning Objectives

After completing this presentation the student should be able to:

  • Summarize the scope of the substance hierarchy.
  • Explain how substance concepts are used to model concepts from other hierarchies.
